title: Martina on Why Pimps Are Important, How She Became a Hoe & More
description:
Martina tells her story and how she wanted to be active since she was a young girl.
https://www.instagram.com/tha_sharp_one/
https://twitter.com/theonlysharp

-----
00:00 Intro
2:22 - Martina on how Don Juan’s party led her to appear on Soft White Underbelly
4:45 - Sharp and DoKnow on the misconceptions people have about SWU
6:15 - Martina “I always wanted to be a h*e.”
12:15 - Martina breaks down the difference between 1st, 2nd, and 3rd string h___
15:45 - Entering the game as a 1st string using all the clothes she stole from shoplifting
16:30 - Having a baby with a Spanish guy who looks like DoKnow
19:30 - Deciding to turn out because her post office job wasn’t enough
22:20 - Sharp and Martina break down how “the ism” has influenced rap and pop culture
27:05 - Martina can’t love a man with no money
28:50 - Martina wants Jeff Bezos to help her be the first h*e to go on the moon
29:55 - The difference between a h*e and an OnlyFans girl
34:38 - Setting DoKnow straight on his misconceptions about the game. Martina calls Sharp “the Shakespeare of this ism”
42:30 - Falling in love with the money the game provided
